36 WHEREAS, the dynamic collaboration of Trinity Girls Network, The Dr. Pat Houston
37 Performing Arts Academy, The Organization of World Leaders, and The Whitney Houston
38 Foundation converges annually at the Georgia State Capitol, serving as a powerful catalyst
39 to empower the lives of young ladies and creating a transformative event that resonates
40 across the state and beyond.
41 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
42 the members of this body recognize February 20, 2025, as Girls Empowerment Day to
43 celebrate the accomplishments and potential of girls and young women and to encourage
44 continued efforts to invest in their futures through education and empowerment.
45 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the members of this body express their deepest gratitude
46 to Trinity Girls Network and its partners, including its Zambia initiative and its consultative
47 efforts with the United Nations Economic and Social Council, for their unwavering
48 dedication to uplifting and transforming the lives of girls and young women both locally and
49 globally.
50 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
51 and directed to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the
52 public and the press.
